Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill allow you to control your Donkey car, which is a popular open source small scale self driving car. When installed with the corresponding extension, you can start or stop autopilot, speed up or slow down the car, via Alexa.

For more information on donkey car, visit the official website:
http://donkeycar.com/
